OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,FFormer Prime Minister Gordon Brown has
OL,7,Fcalled on the government to issue a
OL,8,Fformal apology for the state's role in
OL,9,Fthe "terrible tragedy" of historic
OL,10,Fforced adoptions, in an exclusive
OL,11,Finterview with ITV News.
OL,13,FIn a significant intervention, the
OL,14,Fformer Labour PM said he has
OL,15,Fpersonally been in touch with the
OL,16,FDepartment for Education (DfE) and is
OL,17,Fcalling for an official apology in the
OL,18,FHouse of Commons when MP's return from
OL,19,Ftheir Summer break, to acknowledge
OL,20,F"the damage that was done".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
