OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,FBetween 1949 and 1976, an estimated
OL,7,F250,000 pregnant women and girls were
OL,8,Fsent away to "prison-like" homes run
OL,9,Fby the church and state and had their
OL,10,Fbabies put up for adoption. Other
OL,11,Finfants died due to mistreatment or
OL,12,Fpoor care.
OL,14,F"This is something that should never
OL,15,Fhave happened, it was forced
OL,16,Fadoption," Brown told ITV News Social
OL,17,FAffairs Correspondent Sarah Corker.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
