OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,F"It was unfair to everybody in the
OL,7,Fend, and the fact that we can now do
OL,8,Fsomething, not to rectify the problem,
OL,9,Fbut to apologise for what happened, I
OL,10,Fthink is really important.
OL,12,F"It's important for people who are
OL,13,Fdistressed ... I think that now the
OL,14,Fgovernment has been in power and has
OL,15,Fhad the chance to look at this, I
OL,16,Fthink the Autumn will be the time to
OL,17,Fmake the apology."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
