OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,FGordon Brown, who's time in office led
OL,7,Fto similar high-profile apologies,
OL,8,Ftells Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,9,FSarah Corker that the government
OL,10,Fshould apologise for historic forced
OL,11,Fadoptions
OL,13,FSurvivors of the scandal have
OL,14,Fdescribed the "horror" of life inside
OL,15,Fthese institutions, which were often
OL,16,Fshrouded in secrecy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
