OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,FThey allege mothers were made to scrub
OL,7,Ffloors whilst heavily pregnant, denied
OL,8,Fpain relief during childbirth and had
OL,9,Ftheir babies taken away and forcibly
OL,10,Fadopted, simply because they were
OL,11,Funmarried - the ultimate societal
OL,12,Ftaboo in post-war Britain.
OL,14,FIn 2021, an inquiry by the Joint
OL,15,FCommittee of Human Rights concluded
OL,16,Fthat the State bore ultimate
OL,17,Fresponsibility for the suffering
OL,18,Finflicted on vulnerable women and
OL,19,Ftheir children, calling on the
OL,20,Fgovernment to issue an official
OL,21,Fapology.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
