OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,FFour years on, survivors are still
OL,7,Fwaiting.
OL,9,FOther countries where forced adoption
OL,10,Ftook place, including Canada,
OL,11,FAustralia, Republic of Ireland,
OL,12,FScotland and Wales, have already
OL,13,Fissued a formal government apology,
OL,14,Fand in some cases set up redress
OL,15,Fschemes.
OL,17,FLast month, survivors and campaigners
OL,18,Fgathered outside parliament urging
OL,19,Faction. But so far, their calls have
OL,20,Fgone unanswered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/22
