OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,F"I think it's really important that we
OL,7,Fadmit something went wrong," Brown
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"It's time to make the apology for the
OL,11,Fforced adoption of children, who are
OL,12,Fnow adults, who have been waiting for
OL,13,Fthe assurance that the government
OL,14,Funderstands what happened to them ...
OL,15,Fand is prepared to apologise on behalf
OL,16,Fof the country.
OL,18,F"While it wasn't this government's
OL,19,Ffault, I think they are owed an
OL,20,Fapology."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
