OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,FIn 2010, Brown, who was then-prime
OL,7,Fminister, issued an official apology
OL,8,Ffor the child migrant scandal which
OL,9,Fsaw more than 130,000 children sent
OL,10,Ffrom the UK to former colonies, mainly
OL,11,FAustralia and Canada, during the 1920s
OL,12,F- 1970s under the 'child migrant
OL,13,Fprogramme'. He also announced a #6
OL,14,Fmillion fund to reunite separated
OL,15,Ffamilies.
OL,17,FIn 2018 the government, under
OL,18,FConservative Prime Minister Theresa
OL,19,FMay, announced a #20,000 compensation
OL,20,Fscheme in its response to an inquiry
OL,21,Finto the scandal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
