OL,6,FBrown wants Prime Minister Keir
OL,7,FStarmer's government to issue a
OL,8,Fsimilar apology for the victims of
OL,9,FBritain's forced adoption scandal.
OL,11,F"I'm proud that (my) government did
OL,12,Fmake that apology," he said. "I found
OL,13,Fit reassured the child migrants, who
OL,14,Fthemselves were adults, many of them
OL,15,Fwere pensioners by the time we gave
OL,16,Fthat apology, and we tried to help
OL,17,Fthem reunite with their families. "
