OL,6,F'I've been in touch with the
OL,7,FDepartment for Education myself, and
OL,8,Fthe department knows that they've got
OL,9,Fto act soon', Gordon Brown tells
OL,10,FSocial Affairs Correspondent Sarah
OL,11,FCorker
OL,13,FDiana Defries, who runs the group
OL,14,FMovement for an Adoption Apology
OL,15,F(MAA), has been campaigning for a
OL,16,Fgovernment apology for years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
