OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,FThe group is also demanding better
OL,7,Faccess to historic adoption records,
OL,8,Fhelp with searching and reunions for
OL,9,Ffamilies affected by the scandal, and
OL,10,Fcomprehensive support services for
OL,11,Fthose living with trauma from what
OL,12,Fthey went through.
OL,14,FMs Defries, who was sent to a mother
OL,15,Fand baby home as a teenager in
OL,16,FSouthampton in 1974, welcomed Brown's
OL,17,Fsuggestion of a formal apology as soon
OL,18,Fas Autumn, adding that there is an
OL,19,Furgency due to the age of the victims
OL,20,Fand survivors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
