OL,3,CGordon Brown: 'Government needs to
OL,4,Capologise for forced adoption scandal'
OL,6,F"MAA has been campaigning for many
OL,7,Fyears on these issues yet, to date, no
OL,8,Fgovernment has taken meaningful action
OL,9,Fto acknowledge the injustices suffered
OL,10,Fby so many," Ms Defries told ITV News.
OL,12,F"This government could make a real
OL,13,Fdifference to hundreds of thousands of
OL,14,Flives. We look forward to an immediate
OL,15,Fand positive response and the
OL,16,Fopportunity to meet with ministers to
OL,17,Fdiscuss what is needed."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
