OL,6,FITV News' year-long investigation into
OL,7,FBritain's silent scandal has already
OL,8,Frevealed hundreds of unmarked graves
OL,9,Fof babies born in state and church-run
OL,10,Fhomes across England, with allegations
OL,11,Fthat sick or premature children were
OL,12,Fleft to die as they weren't deemed
OL,13,F"desirable" for adoption.
OL,15,FTo this day, families are still
OL,16,Fsearching for their lost children
OL,17,Fconnected to these post-war
OL,18,Finstitutions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
