OL,6,FNow, ITV News has found evidence of
OL,7,Fnearly 70 more unmarked graves of
OL,8,Fbabies who died at Hopedene Maternity
OL,9,FHome, a Salvation Army institution in
OL,10,FNewcastle, discovered through freedom
OL,11,Fof information requests.
OL,13,FITV News has shown our evidence of
OL,14,Fmistreatment in Hopedene, described by
OL,15,Fone mother as a "like a prison", to
OL,16,Fexperts and academics who have
OL,17,Fsuggested the infant mortality rates
OL,18,Fwere high for a home of this size and
OL,19,Fsay it raises serious questions about
OL,20,Fthe standard of medical care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
